stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (WHY SIBLINGS FIGHT) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Sibling conflict is NORMAL and even healthy when managed well.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (- Competition for parent attention \(the #1 driver\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (- Developmental differences \(older vs younger abilities\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (- Temperament clashes \(introvert vs extrovert\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (- Boredom and proximity) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (- Feeling unfairly treated) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.0 Td (Your goal is NOT to eliminate conflict but to teach conflict resolution.) Tj ET
endstream
