10 0 obj
<< /Length 1379 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (CONFLICT RESOLUTION SCRIPTS FOR PARENTS) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 686.0 Td (When they're fighting over a toy:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 670.0 Td ("I see two kids who both want the same toy. What can we do?") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.0 Td (Options: Timer \(5 min each\) | Trade for something else | Play together) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 628.2 Td (When one hits/hurts the other:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 612.2 Td ("Stop. Hitting is not okay. [To victim]: Are you okay? [To hitter]:") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 598.2 Td ("I can see you were angry. Hitting hurts. What could you do instead?") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 570.4 Td (When they tattle:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td ("Is someone hurt or in danger? No? Then can you try solving it first?") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td ("Tell your brother how you feel using I-statements.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 512.6 Td (When they say 'It's not fair!':) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 496.6 Td ("Fair doesn't mean everyone gets the same. It means everyone gets what they NEED.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 482.6 Td ("What do YOU need right now?") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 454.8 Td (When the older child is mean to the younger:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 438.8 Td ("I know it can be hard having a little sibling. They look up to you so much.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 424.8 Td ("Would you like some time alone? Or some just-you-and-me time?") Tj ET
endstream
endobj
