BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (THE PEACE CORNER \(Conflict Resolution Station\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Set up a designated space where siblings go to resolve conflicts:) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 672.0 Td (What to include:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.0 Td (- Peace agreement poster \(rules posted\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.0 Td (- Timer \(for taking turns talking\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.0 Td (- Feelings faces chart) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.0 Td (- Problem-solving wheel \(spin for solutions\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.0 Td (- 'I feel...' sentence starter cards) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 582.0 Td (Peace Corner Rules:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 566.0 Td (  1. One person talks at a time \(hold the talking stick\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.0 Td (  2. Use 'I feel...' not 'You always...') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538.0 Td (  3. Listen without interrupting) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.0 Td (  4. Brainstorm solutions together) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 510.0 Td (  5. Agree on one solution to try) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 496.0 Td (  6. Shake hands or high-five) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
