BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (SIBLING BONDING ACTIVITIES \(Do Together\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 686.0 Td (Cooperative \(not competitive\) activities:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 670.0 Td (   1. Build a blanket fort together) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.0 Td (   2. Cook or bake something as a team) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.0 Td (   3. Create a sibling secret handshake) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.0 Td (   4. Make a time capsule together) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.0 Td (   5. Collaborate on an art project) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.0 Td (   6. Put on a show for parents) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 586.0 Td (   7. Build something with blocks/LEGO together) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 572.0 Td (   8. Start a 'sibling business' \(lemonade stand\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 558.0 Td (   9. Read to each other before bed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.0 Td (  10. Work on a puzzle together) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.0 Td (  11. Plan a surprise for a parent together) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.0 Td (  12. Create a comic strip starring both of them) Tj ET
endstream
