16 0 obj
<< /Length 714 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (PREVENTING FIGHTS: DAILY STRATEGIES) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (- Give each child 10 minutes of individual attention daily) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (- Notice and praise when they get along \(not just when they fight\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (- Avoid comparing \('Your sister never does that!'\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (- Give specific roles \('You're the mixer, you're the pourer'\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (- Separate when overstimulated \(before the meltdown\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (- Let them solve minor conflicts themselves \(don't always referee\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.0 Td (- Family meetings to address recurring issues) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
